caption.p: Comparison of Spike (S) protein amino acid residue sequence of Wuhan-Hu-1-CoV and SARS-CoV; ( a): Wuhan-Hu-1-CoV (Wuhan seafood market pneumonia virus) and SARS-CoV (GZ02) amino acid residue multiple sequence alignment with hierarchical clustering ( b, c): Prediction of S protein structure by using homology protein modeling ( b) (Wuhan-Hu-1-CoV) and ( c) (SARS CoV GZ02). Secondary structure selection by representing color includes: red, helix; yellow, sheets; green, loops; pink, insertions.
